# OFM Model Agency

- Stack: Next.js 16, React 19, Tailwind 4, next-intl (ru default, uk/en/es), GSAP + Framer Motion.
- Hero: GSAP only; mobile (≤767px) — no blur, no heavy 3D, lighter timelines.
- Sections below hero: prefer Framer Motion; complex scroll — GSAP ScrollTrigger.
- Brand: accent-pink, accent-violet, accent-cyan; cosmic/neon aesthetic.
- i18n: edit all 4 locale files when changing user-facing copy.
- SEO site uses OnlyFans terminology; ad-safe landing pages must stay SFW (no OF in H1).
- Gross total disclaimers on income figures — never promise net payout.
- Do not add Three.js without explicit request (perf on mobile).
- Prefer minimal diffs; match existing component patterns.
